[F]And the men were playin' cards and [C]dice
[C7]So I stepped up to the bar to join [F]them
[G7]What a grand place this Fool's [C]Paradise
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 4}
[Am]It was then I showed to them [Em]your [G7]picture
[Em]I passed it around once or [Am]twice
[C]Then a [F]man insulted your sweet [C]honor
[G7]At the bar of the Fool's [C]Paradise
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 5}
Spoken:
{end_of_verse}

