So I slapped his face and I told him
[G7]I said you eat 'em words mister or draw that's my [F]advice
[C]And he said well somebody might get hurt inside
[F]But I'll be glad to meet you in the street at sundown
[G7]At sundown in front of the Fool's [C]Paradise
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 7}
[G7]So goodbye my darlin' may God bless you
